channel.description:

LOADED: 0 [client-1-uber one]: playerCommand: money [client-1-uber one]: Auto saved game. [client-1-uber one]: Auto saving moreinfo file... [client-1-uber one]: Successfuly auto saved moreinfo file. Game saved for player uber one ClientHandler: Client uber one disconnected. ClientHandler: Accepted from 5.153.119.225:4807 <WTF is all this?!? ClientHandler: Accepted from 5.153.119.225:4812 ClientHandler: Accepted from 5.153.119.225:4844 ClientHandler: Accepted from 5.153.119.225:4855 ClientHandler: Accepted from 5.153.119.225:4862 ClientHandler: Accepted from 5.171.167.133:1454 ClientHandler: Accepted from 5.171.167.133:1469 [/code]
Problem with client handler? it say that then they cant get on problems? help please?[br][size=1]Posted on: June 05, 2007, 12:35:10 AM[/size][hr]It wont create char files or moreinfo or anything files either..

item.dc:creator: @Tico135 Tico
item.description:
@Tico135 wrote:

Is your server hamachi? It looks like your gettin hamachi IP-Addresses accepted… What source do you have? Also, you might want to allow this type of program against your firewall. Either turn it off completely or allow Moparscape and your server source.
